---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'

// Privacy policy last updated date
const lastUpdated = 'January 9, 2025'
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Japan Travel Journal"
  description="Privacy Policy for Japan Travel Journal. Learn about our Cookie usage, Google AdSense, Google Analytics and data collection practices."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>Japan Travel Journal ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-3">2.1 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p>We automatically collect certain information when you visit our website to improve our services and user experience:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>Date and time of access</li>
            <li>Referring URL</li>
            <li>Pages visited</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. Cookie Usage</h2>
          <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance user experience and deliver relevant advertising. Cookies are small text files that websites store on your browser.</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-3 mt-4">3.1 Types of Cookies</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for basic website functionality</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand website usage</li>
            <li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Enable delivery of relevant advertisements</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="mt-4">You can disable cookies through your browser settings, though this may affect some website functionality.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. Google AdSense</h2>
          <p>We use Google AdSense, an advertising service provided by Google, to display advertisements on our website. Google AdSense collects and uses user information for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Interest-based advertising delivery</li>
            <li>Advertising effectiveness measurement</li>
            <li>Invalid click detection and prevention</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="mt-4">For more information about Google AdSense, please review Google's policies:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.google.com/adsense/answer/113771" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google AdSense Terms of Service</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Google Analytics</h2>
          <p>We use Google Analytics for website traffic analysis. Google Analytics uses cookies to analyze user behavior but does not collect personally identifiable information.</p>
          
          <p class="mt-4">To opt out of Google Analytics data collection, you can install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Consent Management</h2>
          <p>In compliance with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable laws, we obtain consent for cookies and data processing where required.</p>
          
          <p class="mt-4">You have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Withdraw consent</li>
            <li>Request data deletion</li>
            <li>Request data correction</li>
            <li>Exercise data portability rights</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do not share personal information with third parties except as required by law or with your consent. However, we may share data with the following service providers:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Google (advertising and analytics services)</li>
            <li>Vercel (hosting services)</li>
            <li>Sanity (content management services)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">8. Data Protection</h2>
          <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect the information we collect. However, we cannot guarantee complete security of data transmitted over the internet.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">9. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>The content on our website is provided for informational purposes only. We make no warranties regarding the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of the information. We are not liable for any damages resulting from the use of our website.</p>
          
          <p class="mt-4">Our website contains links to external sites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of linked websites.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">10. Privacy Policy Changes</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Significant changes will be announced on our website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <p><strong>Site Owner:</strong> Hide</p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:yamazaki2357@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">yamazaki2357@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Privacy policy specific styles */
  .prose h2 {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose a {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .prose a:hover {
    color: #1d4ed8;
  }
  
  .prose ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>